    <div class="row align-items-end justify-content-between">
      <div class="col-6 col-md-8 text-center">
        <h1><%= @chef.user.first_name %> <%= @chef.user.last_name %></h1>
        <p>chef job title (need column)</p>
        <p>chef restaurant name (need column)</p>
        <p>⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
        <%= cl_image_tag @chef.user.photo.key, width: 200, height: 200,  crop: :fill, class: "chef-avatar"  %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mt-3 col-12">
    <p>(need column) Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing, elit. Quaerat dolore repellendus corrupti sapiente recusandae fugiat accusamus, vero, quo deserunt nemo, cupiditate, dolorum nihil libero similique laborum sint aperiam iusto accusantium.</p>
